name: CUÑA VOYAGE SIRENA
campo_tres: Cuña Charlotte Olympia Maiden Voyage en madera labrada con forma de barco. Tiras cruzadas de cuerda y cierre con hebilla.
campo_seis: Charlotte Olympia Maiden Voyage wedged in engraved wood in the shape of a boat. Crossed straps of rope and buckle closure.
